com.ibm.team.workitem.common.model
Interface IWorkItemType

public interface IWorkItemType

Represents a work item's type. Work item types are defined in a project area's project configuration. Types are grouped into categories to which one can refer to, e.g., in order to configure aspects of all types of a category.

Since:
0.5
See Also:
IWorkItemCommon.findWorkItemType(IProjectAreaHandle, String, org.eclipse.core.runtime.IProgressMonitor), IWorkItem.getWorkItemType()
